# ❌ Error: Invoice Processing Errors

## 🧩 Problem
Invoice fails during submission or validation.

## 🌍 Scenario
Supplier submits invoice but system blocks it.

## 🔍 Root Cause
- PO mismatch  
- Tax issues  
- Missing fields  
- Duplicate invoice  

## ⚠️ Common Errors
- Price mismatch  
- Duplicate invoice  
- Tax discrepancy  

## ✅ Solution
1. Compare PO vs Invoice  
2. Validate tax & pricing  
3. Check duplicate logic  
4. Verify tolerance  
5. Resubmit  

## 🧠 Approach
Always start with PO comparison.

## 🎯 Learning
Accurate PO reduces invoice issues drastically.
